304
00:22:05.699 --> 00:22:07.405
(dramatic music)
(Annie grunts)

305
00:22:07.409 --> 00:22:09.821
(eerie music)

306
00:22:11.664 --> 00:22:14.242
No. No.

308
00:22:17.044 --> 00:22:18.409
No.

309
00:22:18.420 --> 00:22:23.335
(eerie music)
(Annie gasps)

